# Vendored copies of webrtc-sys / libwebrtc / livekit / livekit-api are
# regenerated from a pristine cargo-registry copy by
# `patches/apply.sh`. Run that script once after cloning (or after a
# version bump) — `cargo build` then picks them up via the
# `[patch.crates-io]` block in Cargo.toml. The vendor/ tree itself is
# never committed; the source of truth is `patches/*.patch`.
vendor/

# Cache of upstream crate tarballs downloaded by apply.sh when the
# cargo registry isn't already populated. Keeps re-runs fast without
# bloating the repo.
patches/.cache/

# Cargo build output.
target/
